  ///     Mob does not match what is specfied in pDataDef.
  ///
  /// AAFRESULT_SLOT_NOTFOUND
  ///   - The specified Source Mob slot was not found.
  ///
  /// AAFRESULT_SLOT_EXISTS
  ///   - The specified Master slot ID already exists.
